<section class='welcome shadowed'>
  <h2>Hi there</h2>
  <p>We are <b>Barcode Channel</b>, an independent post-punk(ish) band who sound a bit like Radiohead, Foals and Bloc Party (among many others)</p>
  <p>If you'd like to <b>listen to</b> or <b>download</b> our music, head to the <%= link_to "Listen", songs_path %> page</p>
</section>

<h1>News</h1>

<table>
<% @posts.each do |post| %>
  <tr>
    <td><%= link_to post.title, post %></td>
    <td><%= raw post.body %></td>
  </tr>
<% end %>
</table>

